## 📅 Phase 1 — Days 1–30: Discover & Assess

**Theme:** Understand the current state before changing anything.

### Goals

- [ ] Inventory all assets (systems, software, data)
- [ ] Identify top 10 risks and document in risk register
- [ ] Review existing security policies (if any)
- [ ] Map out who has access to what
- [ ] Conduct initial vulnerability scan

### Key Deliverables

|Deliverable         |Due   |Owner |Status     |
|--------------------|------|------|-----------|
|Asset inventory     |Day 15|[Name]|Not Started|
|Risk register v1    |Day 25|[Name]|Not Started|
|Current state report|Day 30|[Name]|Not Started|

-----

## 📅 Phase 2 — Days 31–60: Plan & Prioritize

**Theme:** Turn findings into an actionable plan.

### Goals

- [ ] Prioritize top risks from Phase 1
- [ ] Draft or update security policies
- [ ] Plan quick wins (MFA, patching, password policy)
- [ ] Identify tools needed
- [ ] Get stakeholder buy-in

### Key Deliverables

|Deliverable             |Due   |Owner |Status     |
|------------------------|------|------|-----------|
|Prioritized risk plan   |Day 45|[Name]|Not Started|
|Security policy draft   |Day 55|[Name]|Not Started|
|Stakeholder presentation|Day 60|[Name]|Not Started|

-----

## 📅 Phase 3 — Days 61–90: Implement & Monitor

**Theme:** Execute on the plan and establish ongoing monitoring.

### Goals

- [ ] Implement quick wins from Phase 2
- [ ] Roll out security awareness training
- [ ] Set up basic monitoring and alerting
- [ ] Document everything
- [ ] Schedule quarterly review

### Key Deliverables

|Deliverable           |Due   |Owner |Status     |
|----------------------|------|------|-----------|
|MFA enabled across org|Day 70|[Name]|Not Started|
|Training completed    |Day 80|[Name]|Not Started|
|90-day summary report |Day 90|[Name]|Not Started|

